  m_text: 'Our Heavenly father above hallowed be thy name. To you we commit our spirits
    as we depart upon this pilgrimage you have set upon us. With your sword of righteousness,
    and shield of faith we shall cleanse the chaff that clings to the world of the
    living, so that your kingdom may come on earth.

'
